data.description: Introducing this inviting 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home with a contemporary open layout perfect for modern living. The spacious living and dining areas seamlessly flow together, creating an ideal space for entertaining or relaxing. Adjacent to the dining area is a sizable eat-in kitchen offering picturesque views of the backyard, providing a serene backdrop for everyday meals. Not to be overlooked is the spacious backyard, cantina bar and large storage shed, offering endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment and entertaining.    One of the highlights of this home is the generously sized pantry conveniently located off the kitchen/garage area, providing ample storage space for all your culinary essentials. Upstairs, you'll find four well-appointed bedrooms, each boasting its own walk-in closet for added convenience.  The expansive master bedroom and its large closet are sure to impress, offering plenty of room to unwind and store your wardrobe essentials.    Among the additional bedrooms, one stands out with built-in cabinets, offering versatile usage options such as an office, craft room, or playroom, catering to your lifestyle needs.   Situated in a well-established community, this home is nestled near excellent NISD schools, making it an ideal choice for families. Additionally, its proximity to UTSA adds to its appeal for students and professionals alike.    Recently updated with freshly painted walls and new carpeting, this home is move-in ready, awaiting its new owners. This is your opportunity to make this your dream home!
